Gold Carlyle Watch

_"On its own, classic. Layered with gold bangles of all shapes and sizes, or brightly colored ones, it takes on a completely downtown look."_ -Deborah Lloyd, Creative Director of kate spade new york

* Rectangular yellow gold plated base metal case with white mother of pearl dial 
* Yellow gold plated base metal bracelet with deployment clasp closure 
* Water resistance tested at 30M 
* Case measures 17mm (0.66 inches) wide 
* Bracelet measures 15mm (0.59 inches) wide